<?xml version="1.0"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2010/07/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>jinga</id>
    <version>0.0.4-beta</version>
    <authors>Anup Sharma</authors>
    <owners>Anup Sharma</owners>
    <projectUrl>https://github.com/anupkumarsharma/Jinga</projectUrl>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <summary>Jinga pronounced as Zynga provides a solution to handle the file transformations using simple YAML file as input.</summary>
    <description>Developers often work with configuration files locally like web.config, app.config and during build/release process, these files need to be transformed as per the environment values. This becomes a tedious process for continuous integration. Idea is to replace this step with a simple script, which can handle the substitutions of the variable at any point in time and can transform the file with correct values. </description>
    <language>en-US</language>
    <tags>build, powershell, localize , transformation</tags>
  </metadata>
   <files>
    <file src="tools\**\*" target="tools" />
    <file src="jinga\**\*.*" target="\" />
    <file src="vendors\**\*.*" target="vendors\" />
  </files>
</package>
